    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Boil the potatoes</strong></p>\n<p>Meanwhile, peel and chop the <strong>potatoes</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces.<br /><br />Add the <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiling water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> over a high heat and cook for 10-15 minutes or until fork-tender.<br /><br />Once cooked, drain and leave them to steam dry.</p>",
      "order": 2,
