    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Make the saffron potato cake mix</strong></p>\n<p>Meanwhile, grate the <strong>cheddar</strong>, then chop the <strong>parsley</strong> finely including the stalks.</p>\n<p>Mash the <strong>potatoes</strong> until smooth.</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, <strong>chopped parsley</strong>,<strong> saffron</strong> and <strong>panko breadcrumbs </strong>and season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong>.</p>\n<p>Mix thoroughly or until the <strong>breadcrumbs</strong> are fully incorporated.</p>",
